title: Good Morning Football Podcast: Episode 12
itunes:title: Good Morning Football Podcast: Episode 12
description:
This week: The #GMFB team discusses their weeks off (1:34); Peter never having seen Star Wars (4:37); Kyle & Nate being on the same vacation (8:20); Nate discusses making friends on vacation (12:23); Where will Tony Romo will end up? (19:39); Nate recounts a personal story & discusses the mindset of veterans being cut (26:44); Where Kirk Cousins & Jimmy Garoppolo will land (35:32); the tiers of QBs (36:47); and close discussing some available WRs (40:09).
